name: Steve
text: I like pizza and try almost every pizza place I find. I stopped here, for the first time, with my son about a week ago. I honestly was was surprised at how good the food was. They had a good slection of prepared food, pasta, salads and a …More

name: Mark Larson
text: Friendly atmosphere. The lady was very polite and friendly.   She even came around to show me my pizza order with a smile.  Appreciate it.

name: King Randolph
text: I regularly stop getting some food here. I love the swift customer service and well prepared dishes. Fantastic work.

name: Liam A
text: Had a very good experience in this spot with my friend. The food arrived quickly and the customer service is just good. Prices are fair.

name: Julian Perez
text: Delicious food, quality service, all at a great price

name: Mama Lynn
text: Carry-out order was ready on time.  Staff pleasant and efficient. Food was Pizza Hut quality....good!

name: Mila Wellington
text: Domino's has pretty much dominated my pizza deliveries or takeouts. But I decided to get Pizza Hut instead and did not regret it. Vast improvements.

name: Shohei U
text: This location sucks.  I ordered for pickup online.  I get a phone call from the store and the guy on the phone was rude.  He wanted to make sure I was picking up at the correct location, and spoke to me like I was some kind of idiot who …More

name: Amelia Smith
text: This place is awesome. Had two pies ordered for me and the family, was there within 20 minutes. Keep it up!

name: Kelly
text: Good pizza!

name: Arth Lacanlale
text: Awesome. I love chicken wings

name: Cheyenne Giordano
text: Very rude. Never ever will I ever order from this location again. The guy Joseph cut me off and asked me to call back, I was talking to my husband and he asked me to only talk to one person or hang up after being on hold for 20 minutes. He needs to be fired. The pizza better be worth the rude employees

name: William Jordan
text: The pizzas were WAY over 45 minutes late and the manager when I called to ask where they were was more rude than I've ever experienced before from a pizza place. I hope you read the reviews. No sorry or anything just a bad attitude.

name: Allan Herrod
text: Good price/value/taste

name: Len Townsend
text: Bought two pizzas and both had very little pizza sauce in the pie.  Not very flavor full as result.  Just veggies, meat and cheese on bread.  Not happy about it.
